query: SELECT cd.id, cd.customerId, cd.documentType, cd.fileName, LENGTH(cd.extractedData) as dataLen, cd.createdAt FROM customerDocuments cd JOIN customers c ON cd.customerId = c.id WHERE c.fullName LIKE '%Fayyaz%' ORDER BY cd.createdAt DESC;
